on Symphony Orchestra）发行了现场专辑</a><a href="https://www.nme.com">。</a></p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Cypress-Hill-at-Royal-Albert-Hall.-Credit-Eitan-Miskevich.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="皇家阿尔伯特音乐厅的赛普拉斯山。学分：Eitan Miskevich" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Cypress-Hill-at-Royal-Albert-Hall.-Credit-Eitan-Miskevich.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Cypress-Hill-at-Royal-Albert-Hall.-Credit-Eitan-Miskevich-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Cypress-Hill-at-Royal-Albert-Hall.-Credit-Eitan-Miskevich-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Cypress-Hill-at-Royal-Albert-Hall.-Credit-Eitan-Miskevich-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Cypress-Hill-at-Royal-Albert-Hall.-Credit-Eitan-Miskevich-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Cypress-Hill-at-Royal-Albert-Hall.-Credit-Eitan-Miskevich-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="/artists/Cypress-Hill">赛普拉斯山（Cypress Hill）</a>宣布，他们将在皇家阿尔伯特音乐厅（Royal Albert Hall）与伦敦交响乐团（London Symphony Orchestra）发行演出的现场专辑。</p><p>即将发布的发行版本为“赛普拉斯山黑色周日直播”，将使标志性的嘻哈乐队与<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/cypress-hill-to-finally-make-the-simpsons-orchestra-joke-a-reality-3426267">去年7月举行的</a>伦敦交响乐团的合作永生。表演使他们重新构想了1993年的LP“ Black Sunday”。</p><p> Live LP定于6月6日通过Mercury发行。专辑的第一张单曲 - 今天分享了他们的歌曲“幻觉”的重制（2月26日）。您可以在下面查看。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="赛普拉斯山，伦敦交响乐团 - 幻觉" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/hx8USleUQWQ?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><figure id="attachment_3841691" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-